languages.text: "Что столпились... не видно за вами ничего!"
"Why are you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from back here!"
languages.original_text: "Что столпились... не видно за вами ничего!"

traits.locale_text: "What's with you all clumped together... i can't see a thing from behind your backs!"
"What's with you all clumped together... i can't see a thing from behind your backs!"
"What's with you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from behind your backs!"
"What's with you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from behind your backs!"
"Why are you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from back here!"
"Why are you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from back here!"

languages.text: "Warum drängt Ihr Euch alle so zusammen ... Von hier hinten sehe ich nichts!"
languages.original_text: "Why are you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from back here!"

traits.locale_text: "Was drängt Ihr Euch denn so zusammen? Ich sehe von hinter Euren Rücken ja gar nichts!"

languages.text: « Qu'est-ce que vous avez à vous coller les uns aux autres ? Je ne vois rien du tout, là derrière ! »
languages.original_text: "Why are you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from back here!"

traits.locale_text: « Qu'est-ce que vous avez à vous coller les uns aux autres ? Je ne vois rien du tout là derrière ! »

languages.text: “你们都挤到一块了……我从后面什么都看不见！”
languages.original_text: "Why are you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from back here!"

traits.locale_text: “你们都挤到一块了……我从后面什么都看不见！”

languages.text: 「どうしてみんな身を寄せ合っているんだ…後ろからじゃ何も見えない！」
languages.original_text: "Why are you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from back here!"

traits.locale_text: 「なんだろう、みんな集まって…後ろからじゃ何も見えない！」

languages.text: «No os amontonéis tanto... ¡Nos estáis tapando la vista a los de atrás!».
languages.original_text: "Why are you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from back here!"

traits.locale_text: «Qué os pasa a todos, ahí apiñados... ¡No puedo ver nada a vuestras espaldas!».

languages.text: "Niye dip dibe girdiniz yahu? En arkadan bir halt gözükmüyor!"
languages.original_text: "Why are you all huddled together... I can't see a thing from back here!"

traits.locale_text: "Neden dip dibe girmişsiniz? En arkadan bir şey gözükmüyor!"
